### Setting Priority

<Tabs>
  <Tab title="Manual Priority">
    Set priority for individual conversations:

    1. Open conversation
    2. Click priority badge
    3. Select level
    4. Add priority reason (optional)

    **Auto-escalation:**
    Conversations automatically escalate if:
    - No response within SLA window
    - Customer sends multiple follow-ups
    - Contains urgent keywords
    - VIP customer
  </Tab>

  <Tab title="Smart Priority">
    Enable AI-powered priority detection:

    ```javascript
    {
      "auto_prioritize": true,
      "urgent_keywords": ["urgent", "asap", "emergency", "broken"],
      "sentiment_analysis": true,
      "escalation_rules": {
        "no_response_hours": 4,
        "follow_up_count": 3
      }
    }
    ```

    System analyzes:
    - Message content and keywords
    - Customer sentiment
    - Response time elapsed
    - Previous interaction history
  </Tab>
</Tabs>

