## Conversation Notes

### Internal Notes

Add private notes visible only to your team:

<Tabs>
  <Tab title="Adding Notes">
    1. Open conversation
    2. Click **Notes** tab in sidebar
    3. Write note (supports markdown)
    4. Mention team members: `@name`
    5. Click **Save Note**

    **Example:**
    ```markdown
    @alice Customer confirmed they received refund.

    Next steps:
    - [ ] Follow up in 3 days
    - [ ] Update billing system
    - [ ] Send satisfaction survey

    Resolution: Billing error, manual refund processed
    ```
  </Tab>

  <Tab title="Note Types">
    Use notes for different purposes:

    **Context Notes:**
    - Customer background
    - Previous issues
    - Special requirements

    **Action Items:**
    - Tasks to complete
    - Follow-up schedule
    - Escalation steps

    **Resolution Summary:**
    - Issue description
    - Solution applied
    - Customer confirmation

    **Call Logs:**
    - Phone call summary
    - Key discussion points
    - Agreed actions
  </Tab>

  <Tab title="Searching Notes">
    Find notes across conversations:

    ```
    Search: "billing error"
    Filter: Notes only
    Sort: Most recent

    Results:
    - 5 conversations with matching notes
    - Highlights matching text
    - Shows note context
    ```
  </Tab>
</Tabs>

